content:
#### Single Word Values

```sass
font-family: Arial;
```

#### Multi Word Values

```sass
font-family: 'Times New Roman';
```


#### Fallback Fonts

Separate by commas

```sass
font-family: Caslon, Georgia, 'Times New Roman';
```

<!-- ![](image-l0sxovrn.png) -->

#### Font Weight


```sass

/* Numeric keyword values */
font-weight: 100;
font-weight: 200;
font-weight: 300;
font-weight: 400;// normal
font-weight: 500;
font-weight: 600;
font-weight: 700;// bold
font-weight: 800;
font-weight: 900;
```

#### Font Style


```sass
font-style: italic;
```


#### Text Transformation

```sass
text-transform: capitalize;
text-transform: uppercase;
text-transform: lowercase;
```



#### Text Opacity

```sass
opacity: 0.5;
```

#### Letter Spacing

```sass
letter-spacing: 5px;
```

#### Word Spacing

```sass
word-spacing: 5px;
```
#### Line Height

```sass
/* Line Height is 1.4 times larger than the font size*/
line-height: 1.4;
```

#### Web Fonts HTML
```html
<head>
  <title>Typography Blog</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
```




#### Web Fonts CSS
```sass

/*Import the Font*/

@font-face {
  font-family: 'GlegooBanner';
  src: url('../fonts/Glegoo-Regular.woff2') format('woff2'),
       url('../fonts/Glegoo-Regular.woff') format('woff'),
       url('../fonts/Glegoo-Regular.ttf') format('truetype');
}

/*Apply the Font*/
.banner p {
  font-family: 'GlegooBanner';
}
```
